Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是点根小蜡烛而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And not just to light a little candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天赋，是能够劝服人们…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My, gift, was to be able to persuade people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向神圣的教会捐献\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to give, to the Holy Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是，罗马决定让我掌管梵蒂冈银行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then, Rome decides, to put me in charge of the Vatican bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从来不是真正的银行家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I was never a true banker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的过错{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}，我太相信朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mea culpa, I trusted my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友谊和金钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Friendship and money
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 油和水  - 的确\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-oil and water -Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这些朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But these, friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用教廷的好名声，喂饱自己的贪欲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Use the good name of the Church, to feed their greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要赔了钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If money was lost
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会被责难\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then I am to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿祷告能够…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, if only prayer could,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补足我们7亿美元的赤字\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}pay off our seven-hundred million dollar deficit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7亿6千9百万\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Seven-hundred and sixty-nine million.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教会拥有一家大公司的25%…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Church owns 25% of a large corporation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我说的这家公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know the one I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一大地主\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Largest landlord on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房地产遍布全球，价值60亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}real estate all over the world worth six billion dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要控股，梵蒂冈的一票是必需的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And the Vatican vote is necessary for control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，不不，你弄错了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No. No, no. You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一个人能决定的问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This isn't a question of one person deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一票决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}one deciding vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟世上任何其他公司一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is like any other company in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有董事，我们有规章\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have directors, we have rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有非常古老的规章\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have very old rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:03:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得教宗本人，批准你才行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope himself, would have to approve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已卖掉了各个赌场\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've sold the casinos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有与赌博相关的生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}all businesses having to do with gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有兴趣，也无投资…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have no interests, or investments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在任何非法事业上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in anything illegitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家已准备好将5亿美元存入梵蒂冈银行…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Corleone's prepared to deposit 500 million dollars in the Vatican bank
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只等柯利昂尼先生拿到“屹莫比”的过半控制权\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}at such time as Mr. Corleone receives majority control of Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”能够成为一个新事物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare could be something new
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家欧洲企业集团\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a European conglomerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜有家族空着这样的公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Few families, have control of such a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今日的世界…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It seems in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免除债务的权力…强过了宽恕的权力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the power to absolve debt is greater than the power of forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Six hundred million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要高估了宽恕的权力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't overestimate the power of forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟“屹莫比”的这笔交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}this deal with Immobiliare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你成为世上最富有的人之一\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}can make you one of the richest men in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的整个过往史，以及你家族的历史\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your whole past history and the history of your family
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有孩子们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and the children
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将被洗刷干净\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}will be washed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}600 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上唯一的财富是孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The only wealth in this world is children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过世间所有的金钱、权力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}More than all the money, power on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是我的珍宝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you are my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然为了你们的最佳利益，我将你们的教育托付给你们母亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}although I entrusted your education to your mother for your own best interests
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道我多么期待见到你们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you know how I look forward to seeing you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待咱们生命中一个和谐的新阶段\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and to a new period of harmony in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你们能说动母亲来参加本次典礼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Perhaps you might prevail upon your mother to come to this celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特，我们的名字不在名单上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, our name's not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写上去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Write it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼西尼  M-A-N-I-N-I\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mancini. M-A-N-C-l-N-I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is there a problem here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题，我的名字不在名单上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No problem, my name's not on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你没在名单上，你得立刻离开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, you're not on the list, you have to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事没别的办法\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想跟我跳舞吗，宝贝？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You want to dance with me, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔，乔，这是文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joe, Joe, it's Vinnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼，没关系，他们是客人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vinnie, it's okay. These are our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 抱歉，大卫  - 没关系，没关系\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I'm sorry, Dave. -It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼，欢迎参加宴会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vinnie, welcome to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你真好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次见到你真好，这是我丈夫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's good to see you again. This is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我儿子安东尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is my son, Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣塞巴斯蒂安勋章在天主教廷…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The order of Saint Sebastian is one of the highest honors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是颁给俗世人的最高荣誉之一\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Catholic Church can bestow upon a layman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本奖章，首次由教皇格里哥利颁发\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The award was first granted by Pope Gregory
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生与拉斯维加斯赌场的关系怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about Mr. Corleone's connections with Las Vegas gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料袋中有些照片…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Presskits have pictures of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他跟黑社会的牵连呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about his involvement with the underworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说废话了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cut the crap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇，圣父本人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The pope, the Holy Father himself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派人在这一天赐福迈克尔·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has this very day blessed Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你比教皇更懂？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You think you know better than the pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去啊，去啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do it, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森特   - 干嘛？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent! -Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 她爱你  - 是吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-She loves you. -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，文森，我记得你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi Vincent. I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得我？在哪儿？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You remember me? From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我们一起参加的派对上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}From the last time when we were at a party together
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前去过俱乐部？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did you come down to the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，是个婚礼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, it was a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时8岁，你15岁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was 8; and you were 15
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我15岁时有一堆女朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well I, I had a lot of girlfriends when I was 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8岁的吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}8 year olds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是8岁的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Especially 8 year olds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where's Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托哪位叫玛丽一声\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Would somebody please tell Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅，阁下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Excuse me your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗，你还没给我问候吻呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know? You haven't kissed me hello yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲戚相见总要亲吻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Relatives always kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，咱们还是亲戚？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, now we're related?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的小堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm your little cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲是谁？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你个提示：他是意大利人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll give you a hint: he's Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，我们一直在等你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, we've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住，声音要低，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember now, keep your voice low, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有微笑，别忘了笑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And smile! Don't forget to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸，我好紧张\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dady, I'm so nevous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（意大利语）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多·柯利昂尼基金会荣誉主席\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The honorary chairman of the Vito Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女儿 玛丽·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My daughter, Mary Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我继承了我父亲爱演说的习惯\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think I inherited my father's love for speech making
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是这样的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But here it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多·柯利昂尼基金会在世界各国济贫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vito Corleone Foundation helps the impoverished of every country
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补助艺术家，资助医学研究\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}gives grants to artists, funds medical research
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是致力于西西里的复兴\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and is particularly dedicated to the resurrection of Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔戴总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Archbishop Gilday
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是给西西里穷人的一亿美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}here is, $100,000,000 for the poor of Sicily
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以维多·柯利昂尼之名捐出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in the name of Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要全花在一个地方上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't spend it all in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真为你骄傲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为西西里做了一件伟大的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you've done a wonderful thing for Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们惟愿钱用在有需要的人身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, let's just hope the money gets to the people who need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的部分…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But the most important part
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰尼·方廷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Johnny Fontane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴加入大家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm happy to be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愿意让大家加入我 为迈克尔·柯利昂尼的表彰添彩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I'd like you to join me in honoring Commendatore Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特别为我们的主人和教父准备了礼物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I have something special for our host and Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恰好知道他最喜爱的歌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just happen to know his favorite song.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你上哪儿去？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你最喜欢的歌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your favorite song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去厨房 听托尼·班奈特{\fs12}爵士乐大师{\r}的唱片\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, I'm off here to the kitchen to hear some Tony Bennett records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你最喜欢的歌“他所有的香肠”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your favorite song "Sausage His Own".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊，我正要去吃香肠三明治，就回来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right; a sausage sandwich! I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hello Kay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜，迈克尔，这真是很大的荣耀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well congratulations, Michael, that's really quite an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是贵了一点，你说呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's a little expensive, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了，谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 很久了，对吧？  - 对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-It's been a long time, hasn't it? -Uh huh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 八年了  - 是啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Eight years. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的气色…好极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You look, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子有事要告诉你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your son has something he wants to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为他来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came here for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当律师有什么不好？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's wrong with being a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有，只是他不想当\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nothing, except he doesn't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他热爱音乐 他想以音乐为生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He loves music, he wants his life to be in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音乐很好，我爱音乐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well music is great. I love music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他应该有始有终\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But he should finish what he started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走自己的路\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm going my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己的路？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 专业歌手？  - 正是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Professional singer? -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要是…要是你失败了呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And what happens what happens if you fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会失败的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人总是相信如此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Men always believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有个法律学位，你就有了保险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you have a Law degree, you're taking out insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后你可以想干嘛干嘛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}After that you can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你可以为我做事…  - 我绝不会为你做事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You can work for me... -I will never work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有许多糟糕的回忆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个家庭都有糟糕的回忆\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Every family has bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远会是你的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will always be your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我绝不会跟你的生意沾边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I will never have anything to do with your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修完法律学位\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}finish the Law degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从你那儿来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that he got from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句“不要”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本应该帮我说服他，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You could have helped me to convince him, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说服他干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, convince him of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抛弃了自己的人生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He throws his life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抛弃了成就\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He throws greatness away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是成就？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is greatness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗，迈克尔，因为你备受尊敬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know Michael, now that you're so respectable
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你比以往任何时候更加危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think you're more dangerous than you ever were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实，我更喜欢还是普通黑手党打手时的你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In fact, I preferred you when you were just a common Mafia hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们能不能谈谈常识？  - 好吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-now can we talk common sense here? -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼知道你杀了弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tony knows that you killed Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里是为了什么，凯伊？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What did you come here for, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来保护我儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came here to protect my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是来看你被你的教会装扮的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I didn't come here to see you disguised by your church.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那是一场可耻的典礼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think that was a shameful ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耗费一生保护我的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I spent my life protecting my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我耗费一生保护我的家庭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I spent my life protecting my FAMILY!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，咱们讲道理好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. Let's be reasonable, Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的大事，对吧，迈克尔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's your big thing, isn't it, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲道理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以谋杀做后备\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Backed up by murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，天啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh God
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恨我  你恨我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You hate me, you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不恨你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't hate you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畏惧你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I dread you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽了我所能，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I did what I could， Kay，
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来保护 你们所有人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to protect, all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受世上的恐惧威胁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}from the horrors of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你成了我的恐惧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But you became my horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过孩子们依然爱你  尤其是玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The children still love you though. Especially Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以在这基础上建设\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We can build on that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为他们好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们试试吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你让托尼自由走出自己的人生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only if you let Tony go free to have his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让托尼走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll let Tony go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那双鞋可以用来伤人了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You could hurt somebody with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你工作挺累的，我带你四处看看吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You've been working too hard, let me show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我采访到迈克尔·柯利昂尼吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can you get me an interview with Michael Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，我是他的亲戚，但我做不到\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, no. I'm a relative but I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的可以为你效劳的吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What else can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得帅但没用\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Handsome but useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事，我赌一赌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's okay. I'll gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢赌？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You like to gamble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去亚特兰大城\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So we go to Atlantic City
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的地盘，我让你看看怎么赌\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My town. I'll show you how to gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊，不过我喜欢赢，你怎么知道哪一把能赢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, but I like to win. How will I know what numbers to pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我像个输家吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I look okay like a guy who's gonna lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那人样子可怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Spooky looking guy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的人来迈克尔·柯利昂尼家干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is a guy like that doing at Michael Corleone's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是乔伊·札萨的斗犬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's Joey Zasa's bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识那人？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，我认识那个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah I know that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人，他名叫安东尼·斯库里亚诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That guy, his name is Anthony Squigliaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们称他为“蚂蚁”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They call him The Ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把子弹浸氰化物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He dips his bullets in Cyanide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来表示敬意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came to pay my respects
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我父亲的友谊增辉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You honor my father's friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的教女在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where is my goddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康斯坦琪娅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Constanzia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前我还用这双衰老的手抱过你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was not so long ago I held you in these old hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Piachere? Cominar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，我站着，我站着\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no. I stand; I stand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我已失去全部毒牙，全部年轻的活力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, I lost all the venom, all the juice of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了对女人的欲望\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I lost the lust for women
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在我的头脑清楚了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and now my mind is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对上帝的责任也清楚了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My duty to God is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要特别请你帮忙\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a special favor to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能不能…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的名字附加在柯利昂尼基金会上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}attach my name to the Vito Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你我能在名义和精神上联合\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so that you and I can be joined in name and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百万美金\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}One million dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Godfather
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛，你真善心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello, you have such heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走，我们去品几杯意大利酒\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come, let's go and sample some of Italy vino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈对这些股东一无所知\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vatican knows nothing about these shareholders
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向来忧心忡忡\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a tendency to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已大幅增进了我们的地位，自然我会担忧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've increased our position substantially and naturally I worry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，洛缪，别担心了，我们有共识的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Romeo, stop worrying. We have an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好  你以为我的灰发哪儿来的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good. How do you think I got this grey hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就两秒钟  - 法兰克，你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-two seconds -Frank, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你对游泳池建设的贡献\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you very much for your contribution to the Board's swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外我们需要你帮助山姆·华莱士竞选法官\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And we need your help on Sam Wallace's candidacy for judgeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们总是用得着一个好法官的  - 谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-We always can use a good judge -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Andrew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下，我的教子安德鲁·黑根\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Excellency, my Godson, Andrew Hagan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兄弟汤姆·黑根的大儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}my brother Tom Hagan's eldest boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他协助格林宁主教已经…  - 三年  - …三年了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's been assistant to Bishop Greening for... - 3 years - 3 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期望调任梵蒂冈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hoping for an assignment to the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗马总是有位置给优秀的年轻牧师的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There's always a place in Rome for a fine young priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的母亲 泰瑞莎·黑根\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His mother Theresa Hagen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔戴总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Archbishop Gilday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Honored to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生，你好，我是格蕾丝·汉密尔顿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone. Hi, Grace Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特·曼西尼答应过会跟你提起我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent Mancini promised that he'd tell you about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说也许你会见我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that maybe you'd see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森特·曼西尼提到过她？  - 没有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent Mancini called about her? -No
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝，你答应过我要待在那边的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grace, you promised me you'd stay up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道  - 两次  - 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I know. -Twice. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨露面了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让他在门厅等\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've got him waiting in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说要亲自恭贺并向你致敬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Says he wants to personally congratulate you and show his respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非得见他吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do I have to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说你是他的老板{\fs12}[法语]{\r}，而且他只要一分钟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He says you're his patrone and he only wants a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey Vinnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最喜欢的姑姑是谁？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who's your favorite Aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我会跟迈克尔谈谈你的小麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Today I'm gonna talk to Michael about your little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿你早跟我说，康\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wish you would have warned me Conn',
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以穿好点的衣服来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I could have worn a better suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅乌奇协会选了你…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Meucci Association has elected you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为年度意裔美国人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}their Italian-American Man of the Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅乌奇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Meucci
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅乌奇是谁？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who's Meucci?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是意裔美国人，发明了电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's the Italian-American who invented the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比亚历山大·格拉汉姆·贝尔早了一年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He did it one year before Alexander Graham Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你在这一天来到我家的原因吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And this is the reason you've come to my home on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喂鱼{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go feed the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我鞋子里有颗硌人的石头，柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I got a stone in my shoe, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个替我干活的小瘪三\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A two-bit punk who works for me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个，自以为是你亲戚的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The one who, thinks he's related to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个私生子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特·曼西尼  他在宴会上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent Mancini. He's at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他进来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为我们谈谈比较好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think it's good we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用，谢谢，请坐{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no, grazie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要搞清楚 它是我的麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I want to find out if it is my problem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你的麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}or your problem
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔，你的生意是你的生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joe, your business is your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既无利益也不分红\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have no interests or percentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是外人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm out
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.43,0:24:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它就是我的麻烦了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then it's my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你认识文森特·曼西尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, you know Vincent Mancini
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑尼的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sonny's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.83,0:24:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗，柯利昂尼先生？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How you doin' Mr. Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挺好的，你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm doin' good. How you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 挺好  - 宴会不错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Good. -Good party.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.43,0:24:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你喜欢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，我只好溜进来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, I had to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你专门打扮了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, you're dressed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.88,0:24:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和乔·札萨先生有什么过节？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what's the trouble between you and Mr. Joe Zasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.23,0:24:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有麻烦，我会摆平的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There's trouble. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样挺愚蠢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's foolish of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.55,0:24:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我蠢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Foolish of ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙才有点蠢，你不觉得吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's a little foolish of this guy don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.75,0:24:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.23,0:24:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.33,0:24:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脾气像他父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Temper like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.18,0:24:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔·札萨先生目前拥有…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Joe Zasa now owns
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家在纽约曾经的生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what used to be the Corleone family business, in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出于好心，他给了你一份工作在他的家族里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Out of the kindness of his heart he gave you a job in his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.23,0:25:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你违背我的建议 接受了这份工作\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Contrary to my advice, you took the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.04,0:25:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾给你提供更好的工作，在合法领域的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd offered you something, better, in the legitimate world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.83,0:25:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回绝了我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.43,0:25:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，你俩都带着嫌恶来找我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now, you both come to me with this bad blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.21,0:25:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们指望我怎么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And what do you expect me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黑帮吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Am I a gangster?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，你不是黑帮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, you're not a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.76,0:25:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里曾是爸爸的街坊，现在是个臭水沟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's was Papa's neighborhood, now it's a sewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札萨把它管得一团糟...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Zasa runs it like a disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.50,0:25:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那些女人是这么跟我说的  - 那是过去了，康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-...that's what the women tell me. - That's the past Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.38,0:25:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我靠自己的本事赚得那块地盘\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I earned that territory with my talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.28,0:25:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委员会把它给了我，你也认可了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Commission gave it to me, and you approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.13,0:25:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uncle Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来赴宴的，我不是来请求任何帮助的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came to the party here I'm not here to ask for any kind of help
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.98,0:25:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全可以杀了这混蛋\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I could just kill this bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.38,0:25:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要帮助的是他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's the one who needs the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.36,0:25:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就杀了他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.93,0:25:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事和我有什么关系？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What has all this have to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，他在你背后到处乱说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, he's going around behind your back saying
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.76,0:25:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“操他妈的迈克尔·柯利昂尼”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}fuck Michael Corleone all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:25:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这，这件事和你有关 对不对？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it, see, that's one thing it has to do with you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.49,0:26:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他的面说一次，当他的面说啊，就一次！\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Say it to his face, one time. Say it to his face, one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.81,0:26:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生，所有的私生子都撒谎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone, all bastards are liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.78,0:26:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎士比亚为此写过诗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Shakespeare wrote poems about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.75,0:26:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该拿这人怎么办，迈克尔叔叔？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What am I gonna do with this guy, Uncle Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.97,0:26:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该拿这人怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}WHAT AM I GONNA DO WITH THIS GUY?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.05,0:26:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.88,0:26:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人在城里到处跑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If there's some guy running around this city
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.13,0:26:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说“操他妈的迈克尔·柯利昂尼”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}saying "fuck Michael Corleone"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.98,0:26:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该拿这坨屎怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what do we do, with a piece of shit like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.53,0:26:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他他妈的就是一条狗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a fucking dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.53,0:26:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.73,0:26:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，没错，要是有人说这种话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes it's true. If anyone would say such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.56,0:26:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不是朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they would not be a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一条狗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They would be a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.11,0:26:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与札萨先生没有利害冲突\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My interests don't conflict with Mr. Joe Zasa's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.43,0:26:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你不知道你的利益跟札萨先生有多大冲突，迈克尔叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh you don't know how much your interests conflict with Mr. Joe Zasa's, Uncle Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.45,0:27:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vinnie
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.98,0:27:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要你支持，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He needs your support, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.34,0:27:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我在跟这人混了，麦克叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't let me work for this guy no more Uncle Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我跟你做事吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}let me come work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 替我做事？  - 是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-For me? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.16,0:27:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么?  当打手？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}As what? Tough guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.95,0:27:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要打手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't need tough guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.83,0:27:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要更多律师\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I need more lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然咱们没有冲突，没有债务\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Since we have no conflicts, no debts
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.12,0:27:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的馈赠，祝你如意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I accept your tribute. I wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.46,0:27:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特，跟乔·札萨先生和好，过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, Make your peace with Mr. Joe Zasa. C'mon
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.17,0:27:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，去啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.74,0:27:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂种{\fs12}[西班牙语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bastardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.98,0:27:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vinnie
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.65,0:27:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷，你什么毛病？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For Christ's sakes. What the hell is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.09,0:27:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他出去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.60,0:27:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.29,0:27:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克叔叔，我跟康妮说过时候不合适\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uncle Michael, I told Connie it wasn't the right time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.80,0:27:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.34,0:28:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你现在转入金融证券界\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know you're into banks and Wall Street
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人人都知道你是话事人，就像最高法院\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But everyone knows you're the final word, like the Supreme Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.11,0:28:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想保护你不被这些人伤害，你的律师办不到\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All I wanna do is protect you from these guys. Your lawyers can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.15,0:28:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你能？  - 是的，我能\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-And you can? -Yeah, I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.39,0:28:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么应该担心乔·札萨？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And why should I be afraid of Joe Zasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.54,0:28:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道你不让他在委员会里升迁，麦克叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, he knows you're stopping him from rising up in the commission, Uncle Mike
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.89,0:28:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说就杀了他，你给我命令，我来办\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I say we make him dead. You give me the order, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.36,0:28:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你来办？  - 是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You'll take care of it? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.63,0:28:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你应该…跟随我几周\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe you should come with me for a few weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.57,0:28:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看会怎么样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}See what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.91,0:28:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.74,0:28:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你能不能学点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}See if you learn
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.69,0:28:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们，再谈谈你的前途\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And, umm, we'll talk about your future.
