Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.84,0:37:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲讨厌基金会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My father hated foundations.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.04,0:37:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜欢亲力亲为\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He loved doing it by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.46,0:37:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人对人 但我们，我们不一样了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Man to man. But we, we're different, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.27,0:37:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那些大企业没什么不同\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's no different than any large corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.24,0:37:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以小钱控制大钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We control a lot of money with very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.71,0:37:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交最少的税 不受政府控制\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Minimize taxes, with, no government control.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.89,0:37:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.92,0:37:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.79,0:37:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.93,0:37:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 教父  - 要去罗马了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Godfather.  -Off to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.03,0:37:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要感激你为我做的一切\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted to thank you for all you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.93,0:37:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 来，你要跟我们一起吃点早餐吗？  - 不，谢谢，不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-C'mon, you want to have some breakfast with us? -No thanks I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.24,0:37:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，你的意大利语怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. How's your Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.14,0:37:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要练习{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Devo fare un po'di pratica.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.58,0:38:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他父亲是个大律师  - 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-His father was a great lawyer. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.19,0:38:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没活到看他被授圣职，我看到了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Didn't live to see him ordained. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.58,0:38:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过那种场面吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ever seen one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.88,0:38:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮，我以你为傲，来，我送你出去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, beautiful. I was so proud. Come on, let me walk you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.59,0:38:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德鲁，要是你在梵蒂冈听到什么流言…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Andrew, if you hear any rumors flying around the Vatican
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要让我知道  - 不不，安德鲁是真信仰\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-you let me know about it  -Oh no, no. Andrew has the true faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.77,0:38:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动议讨论事项\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The motion and a discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.49,0:38:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于柯利昂尼集团所提议\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}relates to Corleone Group's proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.84,0:38:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要取得一亿新发A级表决权股票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to acquire 100 million newly issued class "A' ' voting shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.19,0:38:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼资金直接注入“国际屹莫比”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Corleone's capital invested directly into International Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.92,0:38:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家古老而受尊敬的欧洲公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}an old and respected European company.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.24,0:38:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但迈克尔·柯利昂尼有一项雄心勃勃的计划\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But Michael Corleone has an ambitious program
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.00,0:38:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要将这家房地产股份公司扩展为…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to expand this real estate holding company
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.84,0:38:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家跨国企业集团，从而能…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}into an international conglomerate that can...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.34,0:38:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…不是靠政治意识形态，而是靠东部的高效技术\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...no by political ideologies, but by Eastern techniques of efficiency
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 专注，以及不受限制的…  - 柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-and focus and unlimited... -Mr. Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.56,0:39:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生，请原谅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Corleone, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.24,0:39:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你是否将两亿美元存入梵蒂冈银行？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Isn't it true that you recently deposited $200 million in the Vatican Bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.09,0:39:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该银行隶属“国际屹莫比”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}which is affiliated with International Immobiliare?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.27,0:39:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的，有何不可？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is true. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.89,0:39:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次特定的存款在时机上是不是有些疑问？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wasn't there any questioning about the timing on this particular deposit
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.29,0:39:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者，有些说法说…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}or wasn't there some talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.47,0:39:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 主席先生，容我发言  - …事实上…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Mr. Chairman, if I may? - ...the fact that...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.17,0:39:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维多·安东里尼·柯利昂尼基金会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vito Andolino Corleone Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.76,0:39:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼先生的女儿玛丽是其主席\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}of which Mr. Corleone's daughter Mary is chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.79,0:39:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经设立了总数为1亿美元的捐款\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has established an endowment in the amount of one hundred million dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.36,0:39:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔钱来自他本人的家庭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The money comes from his own family,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将由梵蒂冈管理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and will be administered by the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.79,0:39:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这解答了你的问题了吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Answer your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.14,0:39:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位股东同仁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My fellow shareholders
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.24,0:39:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果欧洲和美国能学习一起合作\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if Europe and America can learn to cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.85,0:39:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能学会汇聚我们的财富，分享我们的市场\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if we can learn to pool our wealth, share our markets
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.15,0:39:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能在世界任何地方 打败任何竞争对手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}we can defeat any competition anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谢谢各位今天给我的机会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me thank you for the time you've given me here today
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.57,0:40:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望各位能善待本人的提案  谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I hope that you will look favorably on my proposal. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.12,0:40:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把麦克风给我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, let me at this microphone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.25,0:40:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么能让这样一个罪犯掌管我们公司？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can we let a criminal like thar run our company?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.32,0:40:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他一脸西西里匪相，你们看不到吗？  - 秩序\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-He's got the map of Sicily on his face. Can't you see it? -Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.27,0:40:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是天主教徒就是个黑手党，要我说…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's either Catholic or mafioso. And I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.57,0:40:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主席先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.72,0:40:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈银行感觉…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Vatican Bank feels
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.55,0:40:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国际屹莫比公司…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that International Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.87,0:40:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在柯利昂尼先生手中 将会是安全的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}will be safe in Mr. Corleone's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.95,0:40:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审核及最终批准\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Subject to audit and final ratification
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.76,0:40:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须在罗马做出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}which must take place in Rome
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.05,0:40:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请与本席一同欢迎迈克尔·柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}please join me in welcoming Mr. Michael Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.64,0:40:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，这是真的，这个基金会，它是真的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, this is real, this foundation. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.97,0:40:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前想要安东尼加入\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted Anthony to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.28,0:40:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要你们两个一起来做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I wanted two of you would be together on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.09,0:41:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会干涉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.15,0:41:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你有要求我才会帮手  - 但是…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I'll help only if you ask. -But...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.45,0:41:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这么做真正是为了什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But what is this really for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.55,0:41:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要做这件事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.45,0:41:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要做这件事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.49,0:41:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做这件事是为了我的孩子们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm doing this for my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.56,0:41:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是为你的孩子们做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're doing it for your children too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.12,0:41:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个基金会应该帮助所有人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This foundation is supposed to help all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.39,0:41:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，这是宗旨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course. That's the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.84,0:41:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是合法的，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is legitimate, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.60,0:41:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓这是合法的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swear this is legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.69,0:41:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸，我想要这件事带我更亲近你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dad, I want this to bring me closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.07,0:41:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甘受地狱之火\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would burn in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.52,0:41:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要保护你安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.02,0:42:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不，你去上另一辆车，我搭迈克尔的车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no. You go in the other car. I'll ride with Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.26,0:42:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去去去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.72,0:42:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的老伙伴们 都感激你过去给他们赚的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your old partners are grateful for the money you made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.76,0:42:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…他们崇拜你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They...they worship you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.98,0:42:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在他们很伤心，因为他们认为你抛弃了他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But their hearts are broken because they think you abandoned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.97,0:42:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想要分享你跟“屹莫比”的交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They want to share your deal on Immobiliare
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次成为一家人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to be a family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.34,0:42:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样能洗干净他们的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It can purify their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.17,0:42:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我不能做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.68,0:42:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”必须是合法的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare must be legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.65,0:42:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.27,0:43:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他们不高兴\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But they're unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.74,0:43:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.62,0:43:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己别无所求\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I ask nothing for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.68,0:43:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能安度晚年\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only peace in my old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.84,0:43:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我得抚慰身边的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I must please the world around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.17,0:43:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，你父亲是个讲道理的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, your father was a reasonable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.62,0:43:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他学学吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Learn from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.62,0:43:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从我父亲那里学到许多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I learned many things from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.36,0:43:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集一次会议吧，我的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Call a meeting, my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.76,0:43:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会有亏欠，或怨恨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so there are no debts or grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.16,0:43:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将创造和平\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We will make the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.92,0:43:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.22,0:44:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&\i1}梵蒂冈今天宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.27,0:44:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&\i1}教皇保禄六世已取消了他的周日祈福…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.24,0:44:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&\i1}事出健康原因
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.14,0:44:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&\i1}他的医生已下令完全卧床休息
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.36,0:44:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&\i1}并终止全部活动
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.76,0:44:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们刚开了个记者会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They just had a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.91,0:44:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说教皇的情况危重，原话是“gravissimo”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They said the pope's condition is grave. gravissimo, they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.30,0:45:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}本次会议的目的在于批准…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.00,0:45:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}我们纽约各股东通过的动议
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.77,0:45:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.05,0:45:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本集团代表天主教商人财团\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}our group represents a consortium of Catholic businessmen
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.75,0:45:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反对柯利昂尼掌权\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}against the Corleone control.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.50,0:45:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵蒂冈已经投票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Vatican has cast its vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.04,0:45:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼集团已经控制了董事会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Corleone Group already controls the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.96,0:45:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据拉特兰条约 梵蒂冈的投票必须在这里获准\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}According to the Lateran Treaty the Vatican's vote must be ratified here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.50,0:45:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在罗马这里，由教皇批准\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}here in Rome by the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.84,0:45:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇，病情危重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The pope is gravely ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.49,0:45:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他康复之前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Until he recovers
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.82,0:45:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无能为力\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I am powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.19,0:45:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他死了呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What if he dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.40,0:45:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，如你们美国人所说的…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then as you Americans say
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.78,0:45:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一笔勾消\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All bets are off.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.67,0:45:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们，拜托\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gentlemen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.87,0:45:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是个短暂耽搁，没别的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is a brief delay, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.35,0:46:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下  诸位\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Excellency, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.95,0:46:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建议你们加入大家一起祷告\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I advise you join us in our prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.75,0:46:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求圣父早日康复\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for the Holy Father's recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.78,0:46:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有过共识\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now, we had an agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.66,0:46:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场会议最多是个形式，如此而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This meeting was to be merely a formality. That's all it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.63,0:46:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 请坐下  - 我宁可站着  能不能有谁给我一个答案？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Please sit down. -I'd rather stand. Could someone juset give me an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.22,0:46:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经把自己置于前线了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have put ourselves on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.00,0:46:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”在欧洲传统上根深蒂固\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Immobiliare has its roots in the European tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.95,0:46:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽量理解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.45,0:46:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.05,0:46:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们手段卑劣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your tactics are despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.09,0:46:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，这可是个挺大的指控，来自一位柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, that's quite an indictment, coming from a Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.16,0:46:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们 先生们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.41,0:46:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住你们是在梵蒂冈，拜托\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember you're in the Vatican. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.45,0:46:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要的，是什么东西？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.76,0:46:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，你可以取得控制权\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes. You will take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.95,0:46:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很高兴由你来为我们的小船队掌舵\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We'll gladly put you at the helm of our little fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.10,0:47:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们的船只，必须全体往一个方向航行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but our ships must all sail in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.53,0:47:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.18,0:47:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说得好 你会跟我们一起待多久？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}who can say how long your stay with us will last?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.31,0:47:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是针对你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.66,0:47:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's only business.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.61,0:47:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该懂，教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You should know, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.29,0:47:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.93,0:47:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要跟我做生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You want to do business with me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.85,0:47:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就跟你们做生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will do business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.25,0:47:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒蛇，他们全是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vipers, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.20,0:47:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回到波吉亚家族时代了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We're back with the Borgias.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.94,0:47:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 迈克尔叔叔  - 安德鲁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Uncle Michael. -Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.01,0:47:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你来了，见到你太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I heard you were here. It's so nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.11,0:47:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森  - 你好吗，安德鲁？  - 太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent. -How are you, Andrew? -It's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.95,0:47:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟波吉亚家族有何关系？那种日子过去了，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, what is this with the Borgias? Those days are over, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.73,0:47:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认得吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.47,0:47:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.50,0:48:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚科橄榄油\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Genco Olive Oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.40,0:48:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们祖父开端的地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's where our grandfather got his start.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.23,0:48:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当递送员起家，每周挣3块\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he start as a delivery boy making three bucks a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.70,0:48:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3年后他拥有了这家公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Three years later, he owned the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.24,0:48:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国才有这种事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.24,0:48:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.46,0:48:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，文森佐，你躲哪儿去了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincenzo, where have you been hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.86,0:48:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抛下我们…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You deserted us
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.22,0:48:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是我们最需要你帮忙的时候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}when we need your help so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.60,0:48:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我回来了 我能为你们做什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well now I'm back, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.10,0:48:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉乔·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Get rid of Joe Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.50,0:48:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他卖毒品给孩子们  - 你看，我还是姑娘的时候，事情不一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-He sells drugs to children. -You know, when I was a girl, it was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.79,0:48:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我变老了，倒害怕夜里在街上走路了，知道吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm an older woman, I'm afraid to walk the streets at night, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.71,0:48:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们大概在哪里？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where are they supposed to be at?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.11,0:48:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢，怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lou, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.51,0:48:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经迟了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.25,0:48:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候让你失望过？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Have I ever let you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.48,0:48:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.92,0:48:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.35,0:48:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 再见  - 太谢谢你了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Byebye. - Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.52,0:48:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们愉快\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.60,0:48:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居有些麻烦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Neighborhood's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.13,0:48:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都这么照应他们吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're keeping your eye out for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.74,0:48:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.18,0:48:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.84,0:48:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}From now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.84,0:48:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以来都想念你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I missed you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.31,0:49:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想念你，堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I missed you, too, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.91,0:49:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀念跟所有堂表兄妹们一起长大\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I missed growing up with all my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.91,0:49:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时不认识你，我就想念你了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I didn't know you, and I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.92,0:49:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得我们父亲的事吗？过去的日子？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you remember stories about our fathers, the old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.65,0:49:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得，你想知道什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah. What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.33,0:49:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑尼是怎么样的人？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What was Sonny like?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.30,0:49:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是城里的王子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He was the prince of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.13,0:49:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在我出生之前就死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He died before I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.77,0:49:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我听过关于他的许多故事  他是个传奇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I heard a million stories. He was a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.60,0:49:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我父亲呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.94,0:49:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个伟大的人物，你父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A great man, your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.81,0:49:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个英雄，他拯救了家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a hero. He saved the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.05,0:49:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森  - 什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.82,0:49:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有没有杀死自己的亲兄弟？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did he kill his own brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.59,0:49:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.43,0:49:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那些都是谎话？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So those are all lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.43,0:49:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些故事，亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just stories, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.97,0:49:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.70,0:50:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.38,0:50:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你在身边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm glad you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.98,0:50:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴你在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm glad you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.69,0:50:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂妹{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cugina.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.19,0:50:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂哥\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.14,0:50:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带乔伊·札萨来搭机，然后把他推下去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd like to take Joey Zasa up for a ride in this and drop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.88,0:50:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨什么都不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.75,0:50:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个微不足道的跑腿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a small-time enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.22,0:50:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他诈唬、威胁，但什么也不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He bluffs, threats, but nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.06,0:50:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔着一英里你就能看见他来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You'll be able to see him coming a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.39,0:50:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们应该杀了他，趁他还没…  - 不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-We should kill him before he kills... -No!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.13,0:50:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不要恨你的敌人，这会影响你的判断\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Never hate your enemies. It affects your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.69,0:51:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.74,0:51:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴再次见到你，柯利昂尼先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening. Nice to see you again, Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.00,0:52:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们信任你，掌管我们赌场的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We trusted you to manage our money in the casinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.40,0:52:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20年都不到，你卖掉了那些赌场\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not even 20 years you sold the casinos
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.07,0:52:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们大家赚了大钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and you made fortunes for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.31,0:52:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害啊  唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bravo, Don Corleone!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.91,0:52:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.96,0:52:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  我到这里来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Friends, I have come here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.46,0:52:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}because
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.26,0:52:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们共同的事业已经结束了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}our business together is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.38,0:52:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经兴盛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have prospered
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.26,0:52:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们是时候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and now it is time for us
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.51,0:52:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除我们之间的业务关系了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to dissolve the business relationship between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.43,0:52:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.20,0:52:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我的确有点小惊喜  艾尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I do have a little surprise, Al
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.57,0:52:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位在赌场的股份\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your shares in the casino
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.41,0:52:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我应该省掉所有繁文缛节\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought I'd cut through all the red tape
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.22,0:52:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们直接拿到你们的钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so you can get your money right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.75,0:52:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五千万\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}$50 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.32,0:53:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每个人都一样，取决于多少…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not everybody gets the same. It depends on how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.32,0:53:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没你的份儿  - …是你投资的，以及多长时间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Nothing for you. -you invested and how long for.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.09,0:53:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，这真的很大方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, this is really generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.36,0:53:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，好极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.07,0:53:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grazier
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.34,0:53:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，巴利西，你当初投了多少？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Parisi, how much did you invest?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.81,0:53:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记不得了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.81,0:53:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，上帝会保佑你的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, you're blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.48,0:53:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家族做了大部分苦差事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My family has done much of the hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.94,0:53:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担了很多风险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}taken many risks
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.42,0:53:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了给其他家族挣钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}all to make money for the rest of the families.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.86,0:53:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都认识乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You all know Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.90,0:53:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认他是个重要人物\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He is, I admit, an important man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.46,0:53:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的照片上了纽约时报杂志封面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His picture is on the cover of the New York Times Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.80,0:53:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他获得了绅士杂志的最佳黑帮着装奖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He gets the Esquire magazine award for the best-dressed gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.11,0:53:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸都赞扬他 因为他雇用黑人加入家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The newspapers praise him because he hires blacks into his family
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.11,0:53:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这显示了他有善心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}which shows he has a good heart
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.18,0:54:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个名人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.38,0:54:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.42,0:54:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有一天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe one day
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.39,0:54:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会让你们大家都受欢迎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he will make all of you popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.53,0:54:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事实\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.80,0:54:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更讲究外表\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I make more of a bella figura.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.73,0:54:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的天性\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That is my nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.60,0:54:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也想向合法企业迈进一步\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I also want to make a move into legitimate enterprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.74,0:54:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢从教皇那里弄个小别针\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd like to get a little pin from the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.91,0:54:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，我接纳黑人及西班牙裔进入我的家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sure, I take the blacks and the Spanish into my family
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.06,0:54:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…这就是美国\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}because that's America.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.23,0:54:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担保他们不在这些街区贩毒？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you guarantee that they don't deal drugs in those neighborhoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.43,0:54:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我不担保\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.56,0:54:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担保我会杀了这么干的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guarantee I'll kill anybody who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.80,0:54:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我跟他谈谈，让我跟他谈谈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me talk to him. Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.20,0:54:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能拒绝唐·阿尔托贝洛？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who can refuse Don Altobello?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.51,0:54:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，你…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey, hey you...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.91,0:54:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.48,0:55:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你们所有人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I say to all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.68,0:55:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天得到的对待…毫无尊重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have been treated this day with no respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.01,0:55:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你们所有人赚过钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've earned you all money.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.13,0:55:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你们发了财\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've made you rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.01,0:55:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我只要求一点点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I asked for little.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.52,0:55:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你们不给？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good. You will not give?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.32,0:55:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会来拿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.83,0:55:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于唐·柯利昂尼…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}As for Don Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.33,0:55:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，他今天讲得…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}well he makes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.73,0:55:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说很清楚，他是我的敌人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}very clear to me today that he is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.34,0:55:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们必须在我俩当中做选择\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You must choose between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.36,0:55:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过分了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Way too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.04,0:55:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊，不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey Joey，no.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.29,0:55:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以一起讲道理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We can reason together.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.25,0:55:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.19,0:55:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，迈克尔，拜托…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, Michael, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.86,0:55:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃，迈克尔，迈克尔，消息到处都是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, Michael, Michael. The news is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.10,0:55:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都在说，你已经控制了“屹莫比”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everyone is saying that, you control Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.20,0:56:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“屹莫比”已经在秘鲁洗黑钱了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Immobiliare already is laundering money in Peru
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.71,0:56:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有拿骚 我们都知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and Nassau. We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.58,0:56:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen to me, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.69,0:56:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 迈克尔  - 我们朋友也做了四十年了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Michael. - We've been friends for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.20,0:56:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也应该沾一点光\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We should wet our beaks a little, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.31,0:56:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想和你一起做生意，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We want to do business with you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.85,0:56:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对啊  - 用圣水洗净我们的钱...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-That's right... -We can wash our money clean in the holy water of...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.92,0:56:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.96,0:56:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是暗杀，快走，跟我来  - 咱们离开这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-It's a hit. Let's go. Follow me. -Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.22,0:56:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的外套  - 别管你的外套了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-My coat! -Forget your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.92,0:56:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的幸运外套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's my lucky coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.14,0:56:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的幸运外套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's my lucky coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.43,0:56:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在我后面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Stay right behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.97,0:57:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基，走这边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mikey, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.08,0:57:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，我们离开这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, we're outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.76,0:58:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你干得好，文森  - 谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You did good, Vicen. -Grazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.31,0:58:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老的唐都差不多被扫清了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The old Dons were pretty much wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.66,0:58:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存下来的跟乔伊·札萨做了交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The ones that survived made deals with Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.10,0:58:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.39,0:58:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他活下来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.70,0:58:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在斯达坦岛跟他女儿一起\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's with his daughters now in Staten Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.57,0:58:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他要退隐，回西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Says he's gonna retire to Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.41,0:58:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人撑腰，乔·札萨绝对来不了这一手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa would never pull something like this without the backing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.74,0:58:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是个打手，是个跑腿的，他什么也不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's just muscle. He's an enforcer. He's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.12,0:58:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没那个才智搞直升机攻击\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He doesn't have the wit for that helicopter attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.57,0:58:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至没有那个野心消灭整个委员会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He doesn't even have the ambition to wipe out the whole commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.14,0:58:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照我说我们得反击，干掉札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I say we hit back and take Zasa out!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.49,0:58:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远别让任何人知道你在想什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Never let anyone know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.48,0:59:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，我们…我们传话给乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, let's get a...let's get a message to Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.68,0:59:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敬重他所做的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I respect what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.12,0:59:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后浪推前浪，这是自然规律\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The new overthrows the old. It's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.56,0:59:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能跟这个人做生意？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can you do business with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.49,0:59:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个生意人，这是首先第一位的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm a businessman, first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.16,0:59:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟他进一步冲突\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want no further conflict with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.84,0:59:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他，我决定他是死是活\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You tell him from me that he can live or he can die.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.40,0:59:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特，你闭不闭嘴？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent, will you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.74,0:59:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.39,0:59:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.46,1:00:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能是单独干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He can't be doing this alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.63,1:00:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我以为我退出的时候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just when I thought I was out,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.94,1:00:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我拖回去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they pull me back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.55,1:00:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真正的敌人，还没露出他的面孔呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our true enemy has not yet shown his face.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.52,1:00:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.94,1:00:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.36,1:00:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的糖尿病犯了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's his diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.76,1:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带着他的药没有？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Has he taken his medicine?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.61,1:00:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他吃什么药\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know what he took.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.24,1:00:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能喘气了  - 快叫医生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I've got my wind back. -Call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.68,1:00:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能喘气了  - 好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I've got my wind back. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.14,1:00:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快去  快去!  - 文森特\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Run, run! -Vincent!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.48,1:00:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔向雷电  雷声伤不了人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Run at thunderbolt. Thunder can't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.29,1:00:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无害的声音而已\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Harmless noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.99,1:00:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.64,1:01:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，你他妈虚伪的老东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You deceitful old fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.56,1:01:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔托贝洛，你他妈的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Altobello, you fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.06,1:01:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.23,1:01:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.45,1:01:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，天啊，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God. Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.36,1:01:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳驾\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.76,1:01:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让一让\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Clear please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.86,1:01:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通知凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll call Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.96,1:01:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好，先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.89,1:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能不能在这里停车等？几分钟就回来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can we wait here? We'll be back in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.73,1:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然，先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.53,1:02:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里森先生，你说是急事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Harrison, you said it was urgent.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.65,1:02:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来告解你的罪过吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Have you come to confess your sins?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.24,1:02:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔·柯利昂尼糖尿病中风\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael Corleone suffered a diabetic stroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.54,1:02:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你应该在见报前知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I thought you should know that before you read it in the papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.55,1:02:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.53,1:02:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在病危昏迷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's in a coma on the critical list.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.78,1:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来强调交易不论任何情形都将继续\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm here to insist the deal goes through in any event.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.65,1:02:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇不剩多少时间了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The pope has not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.32,1:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，跟你一样，我处在一个困难的位置上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, as you, I am in a difficult position.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.46,1:02:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得尽快争取核准此交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have to ratify this deal as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.60,1:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我们有共识\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.44,1:02:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.77,1:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去医院\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm going to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.86,1:02:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为柯利昂尼先生祈祷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll pray for Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.89,1:02:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.22,1:02:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与柯利昂尼先生同在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our thoughts are with Mr. Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.96,1:02:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你，吉姆神父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you, Father Jim.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.78,1:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果柯利昂尼死了，一切会被揭开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everything will be out in the open if Corleone dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.75,1:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求时间吧，凯恩济格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pray for time, Keinszig.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.52,1:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个习惯源自…对永恒的长久思考\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A habit born of, a long contemplation of eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.72,1:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hello, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.55,1:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.16,1:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.83,1:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再没想到你会来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I never expected you to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.65,1:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我知道，我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.38,1:04:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.89,1:04:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.04,1:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.48,1:04:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我第一次看到你样子这么无助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}this is the first time I've seen you look so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.52,1:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没那么严重  真的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not so bad, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.61,1:04:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.10,1:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在变得更聪明了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm getting wiser now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.23,1:04:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是吗？  - 是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Yeah? -Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.37,1:04:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你病得越重越聪明，嗯？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The sicker you get, the wiser you get, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.80,1:04:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我死的时候会极其聪明\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I'm dead, I'm gonna be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.55,1:04:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 迈克尔  - 怎么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Michael -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.01,1:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要替托尼谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want to thank you for Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.03,1:04:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做得很好，他真的受到一些正面关注\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's doing really well. He's gotten some very good notices
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.52,1:04:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他就要第一次登台唱歌剧了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and he's going to be making his operatic debut
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.76,1:04:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巴勒莫西西里，复活节，所以…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in Sicily, Palermo, this Easter. So...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.02,1:05:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，很好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.66,1:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.46,1:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是光荣，在西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's a real honor. In Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.72,1:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去的  我不会错过的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will be there. I won't miss that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.66,1:05:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会错过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't miss that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.50,1:05:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽  托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.35,1:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go see dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.74,1:05:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，来，过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, come, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.13,1:05:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 宝贝女儿  - 一切都会好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Oh, sweetheart. -Everything's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.54,1:05:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.84,1:05:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.78,1:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你怎么样，爸爸？  - 过来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-How you doin' pop? -Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.14,1:05:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈告诉我了  你演出的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your mother told me. She told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.10,1:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴勒莫的事？我真希望你能去，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}About Palermo? I really wanted you to be there, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.65,1:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  过来亲我一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course. Come here, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.66,1:06:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼堂哥？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cousin Vinnie?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.81,1:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，他不在这里，要不你打他公寓电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, he isn't here. Why don't you call his apartment
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.57,1:06:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他留个电话录音\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}leave a message on his machine?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.01,1:06:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你堂妹玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's your cousin, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.34,1:06:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她进来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.91,1:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.35,1:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，堂哥\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, cuz
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.12,1:06:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得应该顺路来一下，可以吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I just thought I'd drop by. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.46,1:06:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫弟兄们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna get the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.32,1:06:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，这不好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, it's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.08,1:06:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不应该来的，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You shouldn't have come, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.06,1:06:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能几分钟，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A couple minutes only, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.78,1:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你样子很漂亮，表妹  - 谢谢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-You look beautiful, cous. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.74,1:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的俱乐部，你的藏身处？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So this is your club, your hideout?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.15,1:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.56,1:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I came here to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.77,1:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很奇怪，只有我和康妮姑姑在屋里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's so strange, just me and Aunt Connie in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.96,1:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你在一起我感觉好多了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I feel better when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.05,1:07:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了，亲爱的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's wrong, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.84,1:07:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的被我父亲的事吓着了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm really scared about my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.77,1:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.84,1:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我看到他们把他抬出救护车时  我以为他死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I saw them take him out of that ambulance, I thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.65,1:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道，人人都说他会好起来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know. Everybody says he's gonna be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.44,1:07:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.60,1:07:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我小时候他们扫射我们家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I remember them shooting at our house when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.57,1:07:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔·奈利有一次带了另外一些保镖来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And Al Neri came one time with other bodyguards
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.52,1:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我和托尼带走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and just took me and Tony away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.38,1:07:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是这一套又发生了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is it all happening again?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.97,1:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那不一样，亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not like that, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.79,1:07:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么躲在这里？有什么事会对你不利吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then why are you hiding here? Is something going to happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.40,1:07:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会有事的，表亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nothing's gonna happen to me, cugina.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.08,1:07:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会照顾你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We'll take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.56,1:08:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跟你一起躲在这里吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can I stay here and hide out with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.65,1:08:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你得为小伙子们做gnocchi团子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You have to make gnocchi for the boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.10,1:08:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我不懂怎么做菜，不过我可以帮忙\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know I don't know how to cook, but I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.84,1:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.05,1:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.05,1:09:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  堂哥\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, cuz
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.30,1:09:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你  堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, too, cuz.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.76,1:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，做饭吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay, let's cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.17,1:09:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.49,1:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些媒体人、警察…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know the people like you in the press, the police...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.57,1:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱用“黑手党” “我们的事业”这种词\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}use words like Mafia, Cosa Nostra.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.41,1:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是幻想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.16,1:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们意裔美国人是了不起的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Italian-Americans are great people.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.29,1:10:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们铺下建设这城市的砖块，我们中有艺术家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We laid the bricks that built this city. We have the artists.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.79,1:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有梅乌奇，他发明了电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have Meucci. He invented the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.69,1:10:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有唐·阿米奇，他扮演了发明电话的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We have Don Ameche who played the guy who invented the telephone. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.56,1:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以听好了，赶紧给自己买张抽奖券\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, listen, come on, buy yourself a nice raffle ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.76,1:10:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没准给自己赢一辆凯迪拉克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe win yourself a Cadillac.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.00,1:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这香肠棒极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The salciccia is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.65,1:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给，吃个三明治吧，我们走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here, have a sandwich. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.71,1:10:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.53,1:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 见到你真好，札萨先生  - 祝你愉快\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Nice to see you, Mr. Zasa. -Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.70,1:10:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了去买抽奖券  嗯？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't forget to buy your raffle tickets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.77,1:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你干什么？  - 他不是故意的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-What are you doin'?  -He didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.27,1:10:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉  过来，孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's sorry. Come here, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.44,1:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我们走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK, OK, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.26,1:11:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，你好吗，朋友？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey, how are you, pal?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.60,1:11:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿，你好吗，哥们？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, how are you, Buddy Boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.70,1:11:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊·札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Joey Zasa!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.56,1:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，操你屁股\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey! Up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.74,1:11:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁？你认识他？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Who is this? You know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.84,1:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别理他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.04,1:11:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊，谁会赢这辆汽车？“蚂蚁”吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey,Joey, who's gonna win the car? The Ant?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.14,1:11:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意裔美国人的坏名声就是这样来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is the thing that gives the Italian-Americans a bad name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.05,1:11:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种败类\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A caponi like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.39,1:11:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，乔伊，操你屁股\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Joey, up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.37,1:11:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，你他妈下不下车？你有抽奖券吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, would you get off of that fuckin' car, all right? You got a raffle ticket?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.93,1:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊，看看我的抽奖券，开始喽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Joey, take a good look at my raffle ticket, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.57,1:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要这样对待你，和你的抽奖券\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here's what I think of you and your raffle ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.97,1:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你，快他妈离开这车，我要捏烂你他妈的蛋蛋\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I told you, get the fuck outta this car, I'll break your fucking balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.02,1:12:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你他妈的滚开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.97,1:12:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开，滚开\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Get outta here. Get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.30,1:12:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯库里亚诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Squigliaro.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.11,1:12:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还跑，乔，你这坨屎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Run, Joey, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.57,1:12:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门  快开门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Open the door! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.58,1:12:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨，乔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hi, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.65,1:12:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札萨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Zasa.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.33,1:13:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不准下这种命令\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't ever again give that kind of order.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.69,1:13:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我活着就不行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not while I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.51,1:13:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.78,1:13:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你病得不能做决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were too sick to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.24,1:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我征得奈利同意，我征得康妮同意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I got a go-ahead from Neri, I got a go-ahead from Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.99,1:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Connie?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.89,1:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正确的决定，迈克尔叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was the right decision, Uncle Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.44,1:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是错误的决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.54,1:13:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我指挥这个家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I command this family.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.77,1:13:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管对错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.76,1:13:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我想要的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it was not what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.09,1:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明不明白？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.80,1:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.49,1:14:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.86,1:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.43,1:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  文森特  扶我回床上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good. Vincent, help me to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.37,1:14:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你谈谈，单独，就一会儿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanna talk to you, alone, for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.61,1:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.47,1:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是感觉对你负有责任\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always felt responsible for you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.58,1:14:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know than...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.99,1:14:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your father
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.84,1:15:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥，我们个性相反\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}my brother, we were opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.64,1:15:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会吵架争辩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We would fight and argue
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.09,1:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从未怀疑过他的爱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I never doubted his love.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.73,1:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他愿意为我做任何事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He would do anything for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.00,1:15:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他的脾气\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But his temper
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.84,1:15:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太急躁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it was too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.24,1:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮蔽了他的理智\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Clouded his reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.21,1:15:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想要你犯这种错误\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't want you to make that mistake
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.69,1:15:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Also
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.99,1:15:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对女人也很有一套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he, too, had a way with women.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.55,1:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 文森特…  - 我也这么听说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Vincent.. -So I hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.41,1:15:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我女儿是在做什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what are you doing with my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.33,1:15:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她是怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What are you doing with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.04,1:15:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.17,1:15:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.95,1:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.56,1:16:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincenzo
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.07,1:16:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们动手时…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When they come
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.40,1:16:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会冲着你所爱的来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they'll come at what you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.87,1:17:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.34,1:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·本蒂诺，我的老朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Bendino, my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.74,1:17:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}pap
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.51,1:17:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要带你们来这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted to bring you here
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.30,1:18:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让我的老朋友及庇护人唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so that my old friend and protector Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.26,1:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们出主意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}could advise us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.44,1:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.64,1:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}你对阿尔托贝洛有什么看法？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.72,1:18:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}一个很有才干的人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.98,1:18:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}他维持了我们西西里人与美国朋友之间的和平
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.97,1:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}讲道理的圣人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.34,1:18:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特兰大城那次大屠杀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The bloodbath in Atlantic City,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.74,1:18:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给纽约留下个烂摊子，现在…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}left New York a mess. Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.27,1:18:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔伊·札萨起码曾经经营得有个样子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Joey Zasa at least was running a very tight ship,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.95,1:18:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他出局了，我们有义务介入\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but now that he's out of the picture, we're obligated to step in.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.74,1:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介入回去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Step back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.62,1:18:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不介入，中国人、哥伦比亚人就会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If we don't, the Chinese, the Colombians will.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.38,1:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}柯利昂尼家族不贩毒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.69,1:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}所以纽约弱，巴勒莫强
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.84,1:18:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}你的敌人总是会在你丢下的地方坐大
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.69,1:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.56,1:18:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}谁可能下令那场屠杀
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.84,1:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}同时还能施压梵蒂冈的交易？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.11,1:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}只有卢凯西…势力范围能达这两地
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.14,1:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的船必须朝同一个方向航行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our ships must all sail in the same direction
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.31,1:19:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利政界几个世纪来都有这种人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Italian politics have had these kind of men for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.52,1:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们，是真正的黑手党\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're, the true Mafia
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.19,1:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总主教和梵蒂冈银行，才是大问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Archbishop and the Vatican bank, that's the big problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.56,1:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是同一个问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're the same problem
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.38,1:19:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BJ，他们有勾结\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}B.J., they're connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.67,1:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总主教有一些很有权势的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Archbishop has very powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.02,1:19:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全力保护他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They totally protect him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.99,1:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}教会方面有没有我们能投靠的人？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.57,1:19:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}能把我们的问题告诉这个人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.45,1:19:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}枢机主教龙巴度
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.70,1:19:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}为人睿智和善，极有影响力
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.41,1:19:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}他会见你的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.08,1:19:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}好
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.34,1:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去见这位枢机主教龙巴度\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I will go see this Cardinal Lamberto
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.20,1:20:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们能不能用文明的方式解决问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and see if we can work things out in a civilized way
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.97,1:20:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遵守协约\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You honor your agreements
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.28,1:20:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对付的这些人是无赖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}These people you're dealing with are crooks
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.56,1:20:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不讲信义\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}they have no honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.91,1:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话是最终决定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My word is final.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.55,1:20:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H96D4F7&}政治与犯罪，它们是一回事
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.71,1:20:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩 精彩 精彩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bravo! Bravo, Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.72,1:21:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀请你们大家到此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have invited you all here
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.05,1:21:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆祝我的儿子首次歌剧院演出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to celebrate, my son's first appearance in an opera house
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.99,1:21:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们玩“费城牌”  - 他将于三周后…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- We'll play "Philadelphia" - He will be appearing, in about three weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.06,1:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 7张牌，2张下，4张上…  - 在玛西摩剧院登台\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- 7 cards. 2 down, 4 up  -in the Theatre Maximo
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.74,1:21:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演出歌剧“乡间骑士”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}in the opera, Cavalleria Rusticana.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.20,1:21:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乡间骑士，爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's Cavalleria Rusticana dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.07,1:21:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士 看来我买错歌剧票了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Cavalleria. I think I've got tickets to the wrong opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.11,1:21:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在纽约待得太久了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've been in New York too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.64,1:21:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之，你们都会收到门票\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anyway, you will all receive tickets.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.24,1:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多捧场啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So come on down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.88,1:21:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  我有一份礼物给你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Uh, dad, I've got a present for you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.99,1:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它来自柯利昂尼小镇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It comes from the town of Corleone and uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.42,1:21:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一首真正的西西里歌谣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it's authentic Sicilian
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.56,1:21:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And uh
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.56,1:21:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为你学的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I learned it for you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.84,1:21:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}月在空中烧 我在爱中燃烧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.14,1:22:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}火焰殆尽 正如我心
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.40,1:22:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}我的灵魂呼喊于痛苦中
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.41,1:22:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}无法平静 多么可怕的夜
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.77,1:22:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}时光消逝 但日子不再来
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.69,1:22:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}太阳不再有 只因她没有归来
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.11,1:22:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}燃烧我的土地 燃烧我的心
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.89,1:22:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}她渴求清水 而我渴求爱
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.19,1:22:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}我能向谁吟唱我的歌
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.70,1:23:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}阳台上已然无人现身
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.44,1:23:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又漂亮又善良 我爱过她\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She was, wonderful, beautiful. I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.66,1:23:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而她死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.06,1:23:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的亲信保镖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My trusted bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.50,1:23:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我车上装了炸弹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}planted a bomb in my car
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.80,1:23:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在我之前去开车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}she drove it before I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.47,1:23:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么美丽的地方如此暴力？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why is such a beautiful country, so violent?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.17,1:23:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}History.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.76,1:23:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，妈妈跟我说起从前…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, mom was telling me about the old days,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.87,1:23:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最担心的只是考试不及格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}when her biggest worry was just passing exams
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.48,1:23:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，那时候是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes it was, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.48,1:23:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我为你担心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I worry about you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.30,1:23:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.05,1:23:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，你真是个暖心的孩子，你一向如此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary you're such a warm-hearted girl, you always were.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.74,1:23:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱我的家人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.83,1:23:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是你的堂兄文森？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Even your cousin Vincent?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.29,1:23:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真心爱他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.72,1:24:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的近亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's your first cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.44,1:24:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我更得爱他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then I love him first.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.07,1:24:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，你不能见他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, you can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.58,1:24:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再见他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just don't see him any more
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.74,1:24:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的对 这样太危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's right. it's too dangerous
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.44,1:24:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，听我说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.70,1:24:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能再见他了，不能以那种方式\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You can't see him anymore. Not in that fashion.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.24,1:24:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你，跟我保证\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Please promise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.56,1:24:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.24,1:24:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的堂妹，我的宝贝{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bella cugina...Tesoro mio.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.60,1:25:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要见我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.94,1:25:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.80,1:25:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要你为我办件事  - 好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I want you to do something for me. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.28,1:25:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.00,1:25:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.59,1:25:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入，你需要什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm in. What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.00,1:25:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你出卖灵魂给唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to sell your soul to Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.74,1:25:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To betray me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.05,1:25:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他永远不会相信我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He'll never believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.17,1:25:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.06,1:25:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那要看情形  - 坐下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-That depends. -Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.55,1:25:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个想法\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.56,1:25:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你能不能弄清 阿尔托贝洛的关系有多高层\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}See if you can learn how high Altobello is connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.30,1:25:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安排一次见面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Arrange a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.54,1:25:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你对我多么忠心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You say how devoted you are to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.99,1:25:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他你的问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell him your problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.24,1:25:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向他求助\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ask for his help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.44,1:25:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么问题？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What problems?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.13,1:25:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你想和我女儿私奔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That you want to run away with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.62,1:26:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你知道如果这么做了，我就成了你的敌人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only you know that if you do, I will become your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.63,1:26:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我绝不会做那种事，迈克尔叔叔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know I'd never do that, Uncle Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.26,1:26:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.40,1:26:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你求阿尔托贝洛来找我谈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ask Altobello to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.40,1:26:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以成就你们的婚姻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To further the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.47,1:26:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你们毕竟是堂兄妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But you're cousins after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.84,1:26:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔向来有点老派\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael was always a little old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.47,1:26:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他解释说 你多么不可能参与我的合法生意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Explain to him how, you can never be part of my, legitimate world.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.15,1:26:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你想要自立门户\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That you want your own family.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.46,1:26:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能接下乔伊·札萨身后的摊子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I could straighten out with Joey Zasa left behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.14,1:26:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能够用你的友谊说服他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you could use your friendship to persuade him
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.16,1:26:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远承你的情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I would be indebted to you forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.93,1:26:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯利昂尼家的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A Corleone
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.95,1:26:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂得这种朋友的价值\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}knows the value of such a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.43,1:26:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你愿意为我做事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, then, you would work for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.70,1:26:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Si.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.54,1:26:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吻你的手，唐·阿尔托贝洛{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bacio la mano, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.64,1:27:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Remember
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.29,1:27:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他暗示 要你背叛我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if he hints that he wants you to betray me
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.38,1:27:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有被侮辱的样子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}get insulted.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.82,1:27:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是他的陷阱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Because that's his trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.99,1:27:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有告诉我全部实情，文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're not telling me the whole truth, Vincenzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.27,1:27:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是真的，要是迈克尔没了，那女孩就控制一切？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Isn't it true, with Michael gone, the girl controls everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.08,1:27:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别扯上那女孩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You leave the girl out of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.65,1:27:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你爱她 她也爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Of course, you love her. And she loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.50,1:27:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜中了吧 文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guessed it Vincenzo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.94,1:28:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是位智者 唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're a wise man, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.06,1:28:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟你学到很多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm going to be learning a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.87,1:28:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最富有的人是拥有最多权贵朋友的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The richest man is the one with the most powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.84,1:28:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有责任引介\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's my duty to make the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.35,1:28:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·卢凯西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.09,1:28:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛告诉我 你有良好的品质：坚强\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Altobello tells me you have good character, strong
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.59,1:28:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个值得尊重的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a man of respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.09,1:28:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是送乔伊·札萨入土的英雄\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is the hero who put Joey Zasa in his grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.86,1:28:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们早知道他的存在\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If we'd known of his existence
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.59,1:28:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们根本就不用支持乔伊了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}we would never have backed Joey.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.34,1:28:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人想要再来一个乔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No one wants another Joe
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.30,1:28:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我当你的朋友吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.14,1:28:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便最强大的人也需要朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Even the strongest man needs friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.25,1:28:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深感荣幸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.78,1:28:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是金融和政治人物，唐·卢凯西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're a man of finance and politics, Don Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.51,1:28:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事我都不懂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}these are things I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.95,1:29:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂枪吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You understand guns?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.32,1:29:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金融就是一把枪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Finance is a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.79,1:29:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政治\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Politics
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.05,1:29:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是知道何时该扣扳机\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}is knowing when to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.55,1:29:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮什么忙？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.79,1:29:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文尼？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vieni?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.55,1:29:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信了总主教对这笔生意的安排\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trusted this business arrangement with the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.22,1:29:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信任他，我当时确信他的诚实经得起质疑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I trusted him. I was sure his honesty was beyond a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.42,1:29:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，你也看见了，我现在成了诈骗的受害者\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But, as you see, I'm now the victim of a swindle.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.56,1:29:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在拖延我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's stalling me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.60,1:29:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨额的钱财都到了身居高位的大政客手里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vast money have gone to the pezzonovante in high political places
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.71,1:29:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而梵蒂冈银行就是担保人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and the Vatican Bank is the guarantor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.69,1:29:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你所言属实\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If uh, what you say is true
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.21,1:29:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将是个大丑闻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}there will be a great scandal.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.98,1:29:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这块石头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look at this stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.84,1:29:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它泡在水里已经很久了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It has been lying in the water for a very long time
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.19,1:30:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但水仍然没有能够浸透它\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but the water has not penetrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.79,1:30:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.33,1:30:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Perfectly dry.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.11,1:30:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的情况也发生在欧洲人身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The same thing has happened to men in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.71,1:30:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数世纪以来，他们一直为基督教所包围\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For centuries they have been surrounded by Christianity
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.57,1:30:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但基督一直没渗入其中\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but Christ has not penetrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.45,1:30:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基督没有与他们同呼吸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Christ doesn't breathe within them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.49,1:30:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.44,1:30:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能的话 给我点甜的东西？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is it possible, that you could get me something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.05,1:30:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙汁 随便什么 糖果\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Orange juice, anything, candy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.96,1:30:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖尿病的问题\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Trouble with diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.97,1:30:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血糖水平必须得低\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Blood sugar levels must be low.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.97,1:30:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.26,1:31:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我压力大时有时就会发生这种事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When I'm under stress sometimes this happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.13,1:31:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.73,1:31:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I come to you
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.05,1:31:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这种微妙的事件\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}on such a delicate matter
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.41,1:31:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指控你们的总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}accusations against your Archbishop
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.84,1:31:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言很难\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}was difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.78,1:31:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心煎熬\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The mind suffers
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.14,1:31:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体反应在外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and the body, cries out.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.84,1:31:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.89,1:31:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.30,1:31:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想…做告解？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Would you like, to make your confession?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.06,1:31:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人，我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your Eminence, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.35,1:32:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm uh
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.99,1:32:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很久了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it's been so long,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.05,1:32:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不  不  不知道从哪里...\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wouldn't, wouldn't, wouldn't know where to uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.06,1:32:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经30年了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}it's been thirty years
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.19,1:32:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我会耗用你太多时间的，我觉得\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'd, I'd, I'd use up too much of your time, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.29,1:32:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是有时间拯救灵魂的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always have time to save souls.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.24,1:32:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.77,1:32:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经罪无可恕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm beyond redemption.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.20,1:32:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.41,1:32:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倾听我们这里自己的神父告解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I hear the confessions of my own priests here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.55,1:32:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候要告解的愿望无可阻挡\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sometimes the desire to confess is overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.84,1:32:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就得把握时机\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and we must seize the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.71,1:32:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如我没有悔意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What is the point of confessing
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.19,1:32:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告解有什么用？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}if I don't repent?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.93,1:33:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你是个实际的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I hear you are a practical man
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.46,1:33:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又有什么可损失的呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What have you got to lose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.27,1:33:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.46,1:33:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.07,1:33:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛了我妻子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}betrayed my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.63,1:33:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说下去 我的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.87,1:33:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背叛了我自己\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I betrayed myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.58,1:33:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀过人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed men.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.28,1:33:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也曾下令杀过人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I ordered men to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.26,1:33:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着说 我的孩子 接着说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on, my son, go on
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.59,1:34:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉，这没用\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.70,1:34:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧 我的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Go on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.87,1:34:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.31,1:34:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下令杀死了我的兄弟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I ordered the death of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.14,1:34:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他伤害了我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He injured me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.54,1:34:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了我母亲的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed my mother's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.36,1:34:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了我母亲的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I killed my mother's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.10,1:34:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的罪过是可怕的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your sins are terrible
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.50,1:34:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因此饱受折磨\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and it is just that you suffer
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.29,1:34:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人生可获得救赎\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Your life could be redeemed
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.90,1:34:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你并不相信这一点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I know that you don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.14,1:34:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会改变\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You will not change.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.12,1:35:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&\i1}教皇保禄六世 罗马天主教廷至尊教宗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.71,1:35:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&\i1}于昨晚九时四十分辞世
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.69,1:35:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&\i1}教皇享年八十一岁
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.10,1:35:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&\i1}过去数月来一直健康状况不佳
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.99,1:35:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Connie
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.23,1:35:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一生，都在尽力走向社会上层\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}all my life I, kept trying to go up in society
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.47,1:35:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里一切更高的东西合法、干净\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}where everything higher up was legal, straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.21,1:36:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我爬得越高，它就变得越扭曲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But the higher I go, the crookeder it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.48,1:36:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底会怎么结束？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How in the hell does it end?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.82,1:36:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里互相残杀几个世纪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Killing each other for centuries here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.53,1:36:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For money
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.48,1:36:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为尊严 为家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for pride, for family.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.87,1:36:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了免于沦为富有大亨的奴隶\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To keep from becoming the slaves of the rich pezzonovante.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.98,1:36:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了告解，康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I made confession, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.12,1:36:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坦白了我的罪过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I confessed my sins.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.85,1:36:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么，迈克尔？这可不像你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why Michael, that's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.70,1:36:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必对一个陌生人坦白罪过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You don't have to confess your sins to a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.09,1:36:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为这个人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.80,1:36:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.14,1:36:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的神父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}A true priest.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.44,1:37:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他改变了事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He changed things.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.94,1:37:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.81,1:37:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you know
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.94,1:37:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我想起可怜的弗雷多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}sometimes I think of poor Fredo
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.89,1:37:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溺亡\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}drowned.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.89,1:37:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是天意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.52,1:37:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个可怕的意外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It was a terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.09,1:37:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它结束了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.37,1:37:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.37,1:37:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远会帮你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll always help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.84,1:37:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.18,1:38:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}唐·阿尔托贝洛  太荣幸了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.02,1:38:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}你还从巴勒莫来探望我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.50,1:38:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}嘿，那个小孩，他长大了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.21,1:38:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}给我学个毛驴
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.53,1:38:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}离我们当初一起做买卖有些日子了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.59,1:39:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}套一句美国话 你是我“盖着的王牌”
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.76,1:39:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}我鞋里有颗硌脚的石头
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.94,1:39:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}你能帮我除掉
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.84,1:39:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93CFE0&}只有一个吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.85,1:39:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.61,1:39:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康妮，你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, Connie! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.99,1:39:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽  好想你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.45,1:39:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦，你好，迈克尔  - 你好，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Well, hello Michael. -Hello Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.72,1:39:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 看这个\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mom, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.52,1:39:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"乡间骑士"\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.26,1:39:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，道格拉斯不能来太可惜了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know it's too bad that Douglas couldn't be with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.53,1:39:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不，我知道，他很想来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, no, I know. He wanted to come very much,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.65,1:39:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他有一场重要的官司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but he had a very important trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.45,1:39:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道他一定想来  - 我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-I know he wanted to come. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.51,1:40:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在，你儿子是个艺术家了，嗯？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, your son's an artist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.58,1:40:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  应该谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh yes. Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.28,1:40:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, what for?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.32,1:40:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢你逼我放他走\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For making me, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.92,1:40:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过这么多年…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}After all these years
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.32,1:40:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于第一次来到西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}here I am in Sicily for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.66,1:40:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拍张你俩在一起的照片\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want to get a picture of you together.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.04,1:40:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.96,1:40:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，爸爸，微笑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey dad, smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.10,1:40:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你还带着艾尔·奈利，为什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I see you still have Al Neri. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.21,1:40:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我需要他，他帮我上下车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I need him. He helps me get in and out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.91,1:40:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我提公事包\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Carry my briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.14,1:40:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在撒谎，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're still a liar Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.97,1:40:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你看看西西里，真正的西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let me show you Sicily. The real Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.48,1:40:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以稍微多了解一点家族历史\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Maybe you'll understand the family history a little better.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.45,1:40:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦，我认为我了解已经够多了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh I think I understand it well enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.09,1:41:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Take them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.74,1:41:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安东尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Anthony
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.48,1:41:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件东西，是你很久前给我的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have something you made for me a very long time ago
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.45,1:41:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会给你带来好运\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It may bring you luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.35,1:42:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你保留着它？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You saved it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.16,1:42:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你还记得吗？  - 我记得\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Remember? -I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.90,1:42:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.17,1:42:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你骄傲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.57,1:42:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 爸爸\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.22,1:42:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有外表那么厉害吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Are they as good as they look?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.36,1:42:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更厉害，他们是最好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're better. They're the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.73,1:42:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他们在身边，迈克尔叔叔一定安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}As long as they're around, Uncle Michael is safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.26,1:42:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.50,1:42:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你父亲我回来吃晚饭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell your father I'll be back for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.14,1:42:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.05,1:42:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好玩\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.19,1:42:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉托尼一定要等我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And tell Tony to be sure to wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.87,1:42:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的，我会的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay. I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.79,1:42:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  妈妈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Bye mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.87,1:42:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好，女士{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Buon giorno, Signora.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.78,1:42:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您吩咐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}At your service
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.42,1:43:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我见到爸爸，会告诉他你走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If I see dad, I'll tell him you left
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.69,1:43:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这家族里剩下唯一有我父亲那种力量的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You are the only one left in this family with my father's strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.57,1:43:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如迈克尔出了什么事，我要你还击\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If anything happens to Michael, I want you to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.65,1:43:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让人准备好一切\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll have everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.13,1:43:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发誓？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You swear?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.19,1:43:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你发誓\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swear to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.16,1:44:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.51,1:44:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲出生的房子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The house where my father was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.26,1:44:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是来这里…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is where they came
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.40,1:44:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要带走还是孩子的他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to take him when he was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.81,1:44:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀了他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.94,1:44:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.45,1:44:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.43,1:44:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗，玛丽恋爱了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, Mary's in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.93,1:44:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，我知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.80,1:44:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一个英俊的意大利男人，黑眼睛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}With a handsome young Italian man. Dark eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.11,1:44:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会允许的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I won't allow it
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.61,1:45:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是错误的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.38,1:45:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错误而且危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's wrong and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.64,1:45:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8DD3F7&}哦，父亲，我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.17,1:45:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8DD3F7&}给我一点时间向主祈祷
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.71,1:45:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8DD3F7&}卡里尼男爵夫人对丈夫不贞
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.34,1:45:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8DD3F7&}同她的堂兄相恋
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.48,1:45:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8DD3F7&}这不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.79,1:45:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8DD3F7&}她的父亲刺穿了她的心
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.78,1:45:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名誉，是吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Honor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.00,1:46:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗，我想起那次你来我父母家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, I remember the time that you came to my parent's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.89,1:46:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我带进房间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you took me into that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.76,1:46:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你的家族生意…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you told me about the family business
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.52,1:46:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你是如何不会跟它有任何牵连\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and how you were never going to have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.26,1:46:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那口气就像托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You sounded like Tony
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.83,1:46:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时是很像托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was a lot like Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.36,1:46:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我几乎看不见他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I can barely see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.57,1:46:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 凯伊  - 什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Kay. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.61,1:46:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来开车吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you mind driving?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.52,1:46:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行，怎么了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.00,1:46:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛，有时侯还好，不过…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My eyes. Sometimes they're all right. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.80,1:46:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有，我得去见唐·汤马西诺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, I have to see Don Tommasino
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.44,1:46:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，夫人{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Benday, signora.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.31,1:46:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没有随身保镖啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There's no bodyguards today.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.28,1:46:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是偷跑出来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really snuck away.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.92,1:46:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H90C8EE&}神父，你们去哪儿？要搭便车吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.44,1:47:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H90C8EE&}我认得你，你是蒙特莱普家的莫斯卡
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.24,1:47:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H90C8EE&}以前当过杀手，现在也是杀手
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.94,1:47:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H90C8EE&}等等，我知道迈克尔·柯利昂尼在你家
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.58,1:47:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H90C8EE&}我会跟着你通过大门
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.13,1:47:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.84,1:47:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯伊，这是卡洛，我的老朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Kay, this is Calo, my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.85,1:47:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前的一个保镖\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}One of my bodyguards in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.95,1:47:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们可以在这里等他  - 要喝一杯吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-We can wait here. -You want drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.48,1:47:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我们进去？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.04,1:47:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这房间度过了很多时间\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I spent a lot of time in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.10,1:48:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.10,1:48:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你结婚了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then you got married.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.00,1:48:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然想着你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I still thought of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.46,1:48:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个房间里有什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's in that room?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.08,1:48:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这对你很危险，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know this is dangerous for you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.77,1:48:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是西西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.78,1:48:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱这地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.32,1:48:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.27,1:48:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个历史上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, all through history
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.37,1:48:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有可怕的事情发生在这些人身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}terrible things have happened to these people.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.65,1:48:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕而不公的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Terrible injustice.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.86,1:48:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们依旧期待好的…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But they still expect good
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.97,1:48:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是坏事情发生在自己身上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}rather than bad will happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.35,1:48:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我和你？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sort of like me and you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.42,1:48:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How so?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.54,1:48:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然在这里，对吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well I'm still here, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.91,1:48:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有糟糕的过去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We do have a bad history
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.29,1:48:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是在这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.45,1:49:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，你还在，但心存畏惧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh yes you are. But with dread.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.72,1:49:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下命令吧，来吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gimme the order! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.14,1:49:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么意义呢？这样能让我不畏惧你？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's that supposed to do, is that supposed to make me not dread you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.53,1:49:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在西西里，歌剧嘛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We’re in Sicily, the opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.35,1:49:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.17,1:49:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.88,1:49:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲道理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.45,1:49:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们努力不要互相伤害\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's try not to hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.42,1:49:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你原谅我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.33,1:49:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.70,1:49:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.14,1:49:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢，像上帝那样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, like God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.94,1:49:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，我需要更为亲近些\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, I, I need something a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.51,1:50:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能理解那些日子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You couldn’t understand, back in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.18,1:50:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱我的父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love my father
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.32,1:50:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾发誓不会成为他那样的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swore I would never be, a man like him
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.29,1:50:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我爱他  而他有危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but I loved him. And he was in danger
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.09,1:50:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.69,1:50:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后来，你有危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And then later, you were in danger.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.36,1:50:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的孩子们，有危险，我能怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our children, were in danger. what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.63,1:50:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们全是我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You were all that I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.53,1:50:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上最爱、最珍惜的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...loved, valued, most in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.21,1:50:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我正要失去你，最终失去了你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And, I'm losing you, I lost you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.81,1:50:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're gone
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.68,1:50:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切成了徒劳\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and it was all for nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.16,1:50:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}so
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.19,1:50:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须理解，我…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}you have to understand, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.93,1:50:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时计划了整个不一样的命运\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I had a whole different destiny planned.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.86,1:50:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我不说了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, I'll stop
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.31,1:51:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不知道你要我怎么做，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really don’t know what you want from me, Michael
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.31,1:51:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I really don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.68,1:51:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I mean
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.48,1:51:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是你想像的那种人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm not the man that you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.70,1:51:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.02,1:51:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你，凯伊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I love you, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.96,1:51:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再畏惧我了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't dread me, anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.83,1:51:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.13,1:51:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西西里这里的每一个晚上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}every night here in Sicily
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.81,1:51:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做梦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I dream
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.88,1:51:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦见我的妻子和我的孩子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}about my wife and my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.41,1:51:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如何失去了他们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And how I lost them.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.52,1:51:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…如果这能有所安慰的话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guess, if it's any consolation
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.18,1:51:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你知道…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want you to know that
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.73,1:51:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.13,1:52:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直爱你，迈克尔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always loved you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.03,1:52:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你知道吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.43,1:52:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直，一直爱下去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I always, I always will.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.56,1:52:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}怎么了？出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.32,1:52:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}他们发现唐·汤马西诺中枪了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.24,1:52:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}他死了？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.29,1:52:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}我的主人死了，血债要血偿
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.32,1:52:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}我一定要报仇
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.01,1:53:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}有一天，你可能的为我办一件难事
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.51,1:53:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.16,1:53:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H93D1F3&}我会为他报仇的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.04,1:53:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Siri
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.31,1:53:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙巴度\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lamberto
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.43,1:53:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗塞德\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lorscheider
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.51,1:53:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H83C8F2&}总计
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.10,1:53:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H83C8F2&}罗塞德  1票
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.20,1:53:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H83C8F2&}西里  11票
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.88,1:53:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H83C8F2&}龙巴度  99票
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.47,1:53:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H87CCF1&}你是否接受推举担任教皇至尊？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.30,1:53:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H87CCF1&}上帝明鉴  赐福吾同僚之决策
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.06,1:53:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H87CCF1&}我接受
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.94,1:54:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H87CCF1&}你希望以何名义为称号？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.90,1:54:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H87CCF1&}若望·保禄一世
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.50,1:54:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H87CCF1&}我将即刻执事 而不愿有所拖延
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.67,1:54:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}弗雷德里克·凯恩济格，过去十年里的“上帝的银行家”\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Frederik Keinszig, known for a decade as "God's banker,"
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.25,1:54:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}被报告失踪，最后被见于3天前\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has been reported missing. He was last seen three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.11,1:54:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}离开梵蒂冈所有的“屹莫比国际”公司在罗马的办公室\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}leaving the Rome offices of the Vatican owned corporation International Immobiliare.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.55,1:54:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}随之失踪的还有大笔款项 及多份文件\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Also missing was a large sum of money, and several documents.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.52,1:55:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接啊，凯恩济格，你这蠢货\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Keinszig, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.03,1:55:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}凯恩济格先生的失踪\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mr. Keinszig's absence
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.80,1:55:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}引起了对梵蒂冈银行交易的更多疑窦\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}casts further suspicion on the dealings of the Vatican bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.20,1:55:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}多年以来该银行及其下属子公司\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}For several years the bank and its subsidiary companies
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.07,1:55:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}一直被指为不名誉商业活动的对象\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}have been the object of allegations of disreputable business practices.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.22,1:55:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}这些活动包括…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}These practices include...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.78,1:55:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢凯西  请你尽量要了解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lucchesi, will you please try and understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.15,1:55:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打电话找过他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have phoned him.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.02,1:55:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直在等他的电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I have waited here by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.42,1:55:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要记住，卢凯西先生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You would do well to remember, Mr. Lucchesi
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.45,1:55:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一位教皇\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that this Pope
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.91,1:55:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与上一位有着非常不一样的想法\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}has very, different ideas from the last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.86,1:55:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见，我的老朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Goodbye my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.82,1:56:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I swear
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.13,1:56:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我子女的性命发誓\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}on the lives of my children
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.92,1:56:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一个机会挽回自己\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give me a chance to redeem myself
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.59,1:56:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将不再犯下罪过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and I will sin, no more.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.42,1:56:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不单是一次糟糕的银行交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's not just a bad banking deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.12,1:56:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人就是屠夫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}These guys are butchers.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.26,1:56:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪些人？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What guys?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.23,1:57:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卢凯西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Lucchesi.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.76,1:57:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他控制了他们全体\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He controls all of them
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.30,1:57:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Altobello,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.87,1:57:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总主教\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}the Archbishop
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.48,1:57:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更高的人，也许有P2{\fs12}[不懂啥意思]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}other people higher up, P2, maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.36,1:57:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的，未知的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Secret, unknown.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.57,1:57:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在操作事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're running things.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.04,1:57:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挡了他们的路\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm in their way.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.27,1:57:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.95,1:57:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他雇了个职业杀手要杀你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's hired a professional assassin to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.51,1:57:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西西里人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's Sicilian.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.08,1:57:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道名字\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know his name,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.18,1:57:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但据说他从未失过手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but they say he never fails.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.60,1:57:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁也不安全了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then no one is safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.58,1:57:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连新教皇也很危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Even the new pope is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.18,1:57:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有时间，我们能预防\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We still have time. We can prevent this.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.51,1:57:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I tried
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.11,1:57:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincen
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.01,1:57:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I tried
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.08,1:57:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要避免一切走到这一步\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}to keep everything from coming to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.02,1:58:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是不可能\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But it's not possible,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.96,1:58:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界不可能\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}not in this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.22,1:58:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下命令吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give me the order.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.76,1:58:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就没有回头路了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You won't be able to go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.02,1:58:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会像我一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You'll be like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.60,1:58:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.96,1:58:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一辈子都想退出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All my life I wanted out.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.80,1:58:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想要家族退出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanted the family out.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.93,1:58:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想退出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I don't want out.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.31,1:58:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要权力来维系家族\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I want the power to preserve the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.78,1:58:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请求你下命令\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm asking for the order.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.75,1:58:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再做下去了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I can't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.70,1:59:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.15,1:59:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特知道该做什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincent knows what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.95,1:59:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，出去吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.67,1:59:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下，别再费心了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Take a rest and don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.20,1:59:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的就是为大家费心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All I do is think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.79,1:59:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你的儿子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.34,1:59:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有事情都交给我吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Command me in all things.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.69,1:59:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃我女儿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Give up my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.64,1:59:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你要付的代价\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's the price you pay
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.96,1:59:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你选择的人生\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}for the life you choose.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.52,1:59:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侄子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Nephew
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.24,1:59:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此刻起\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}from this moment on
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.03,2:00:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可自称文森特·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}call yourself Vincent Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.66,2:00:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Vincenzo.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.50,2:00:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}，康妮\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Grazie Connie.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.10,2:00:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.21,2:00:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·文森佐·柯利昂尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Vincenzo Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.32,2:01:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.55,2:01:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（“乡间骑士”歌剧）
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.90,2:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森佐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Et Tu, Vincenzo
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.52,2:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解你对迈克尔的感情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I know how you feel about Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.56,2:02:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你救不了他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}but you, you can't save him.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.06,2:02:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他迷失了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's lost.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.00,2:02:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为自己考虑一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Think of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.97,2:02:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的答案是什么，文森特？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's your answer, Vincent?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.64,2:02:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好欣赏歌剧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Enjoy the opera.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.37,2:02:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都安排好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's all taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.68,2:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查酒吧，我去检查屋顶\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Check the bar. I'll check the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.36,2:02:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿安东尼在马克西莫剧院演唱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here's hoping Tony sings better at Theatre Maximo
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.39,2:02:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜过他在洗澡时的歌声\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}than he does in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.13,2:02:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的康斯坦琪娅\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}My darling, Constanzia.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.79,2:03:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·阿尔托贝洛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, Don Altobello.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.67,2:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个大场面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is a great occasion.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.33,2:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  坐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.11,2:03:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.38,2:03:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你80岁了，看起来没超过60\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're eighty years old。 You don't look more than sixty.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.95,2:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是唯一记得的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're the only one who remembered.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.25,2:03:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，我们刚收到消息\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, we just got the word.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.09,2:03:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇批准了“屹莫比”的交易\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope's ratified the Immobiliare deal.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.94,2:03:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We've won.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.59,2:03:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.02,2:03:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世事多么难料\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How strange, the way things work.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.61,2:03:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇在做的正是你说他会做的事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The Pope's doing exactly what you said he'd do
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.36,2:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在清理门户\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he's cleaning house.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.34,2:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该小心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.45,2:03:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个诚实的人会有危险\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's dangerous to be an honest man.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.64,2:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加派人手到后台保护托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I wanna put a little more muscle backstage with Tony
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.85,2:04:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前过生日总请我吃东西\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}On your birthday, you used to shower me with treats.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.26,2:04:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶油卷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tootsie Rolls!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.93,2:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作这些奶油卷的修女发誓缄口\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The nuns who made these cannolis took a vow of silence.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.60,2:04:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最优质的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're the very finest.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.24,2:04:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂妹\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, coz.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.85,2:04:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的皮衣呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where's your leather?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.81,2:04:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.22,2:04:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么瘦，你来吃\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're so thin. You eat it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.18,2:04:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好，谢谢，谢谢{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}E buono. Grazie, grazie.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.38,2:05:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了，玛丽\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's over, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.72,2:05:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事情不得不做，你不能参与\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There are things I have to do that you can't be a part of.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.87,2:05:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看你父亲，这不是你父亲的决定，是我的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't look at your father, it's not your father's decision, it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.54,2:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要恨你父亲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don't hate your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.97,2:05:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事情我要参与，你不能在身边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}There are things I'm going to be part of, you can't be around.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.50,2:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚之后，你再也见不到我了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}After tonight, you won't see me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.21,2:05:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.71,2:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得理解，玛丽，你得理解\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You gotta understand, Mary. You gotta understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.35,2:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远爱你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.14,2:05:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱别人吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Love somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.66,2:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬托尼  敬托尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}To Tony! To Tony!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.19,2:09:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会做什么了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They won't try anything
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.44,2:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对，一切正常，这边都安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, everything’s fine. It's all clear out here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.19,2:09:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经派艾尔·奈利去了梵蒂冈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've already sent Al Neri to the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.42,2:09:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H92D7F1&}- 卢凯西先生的房子？  - 是
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.64,2:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H92D7F1&}我带来迈克尔·柯利昂尼的口信
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.27,2:09:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H92D7F1&}让他进来
Dialogue: 0,2:11:28.71,2:11:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H92D7F1&}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.63,2:14:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你搞掂他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Good, you got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.86,2:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上柯利昂尼家族要算帐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tonight the Corleone family settles its accounts.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:49.57,2:15:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯恩济格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Keinszig
Dialogue: 0,2:15:51.87,2:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个他妈的瑞士小银行家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}that little Swiss banker fuck
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.74,2:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从一开始就在玩弄每一个人，操他妈的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he's been swindling everyone from the beginning. Fuck 'im.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:00.86,2:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐·卢凯西，我的朋友\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Don Lucchesi. My friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.75,2:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛会去拜访他，在他家\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Calo will pay him a visit at his home.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.05,2:16:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈利\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Neri
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.92,2:16:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭火车去罗马\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}take a train to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.89,2:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为总主教点一根蜡烛\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Light a candle for the Archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.02,2:16:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H91D5FC&}茶，陛下，有助于你的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,2:17:18.05,2:17:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H91D5FC&}这是文森特·柯利昂尼给你的
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.37,2:18:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克尔，事情严重\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Michael, it's serious.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.65,2:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在梵蒂冈内部的人说 有人要暗算教宗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Our man inside the Vatican says there's a plot against the Pope.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.39,2:18:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说晚上他会发心脏病？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You mean he's going to have a heart attack in the night.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:33.80,2:18:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位教皇有强大的敌人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This Pope has powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.34,2:18:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能没法及时救他了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We may not be in time to save him.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:41.83,2:18:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们回去看歌剧吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Now let's go back to the opera.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:10.37,2:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H9AD5F3&}陛下
Dialogue: 0,2:19:12.45,2:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教皇陛下{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.31,2:19:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H9AD5F3&}至圣？
Dialogue: 0,2:19:25.41,2:19:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至圣？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Eminenza?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:28.05,2:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至圣？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Eminenza?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:35.34,2:19:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H9AD5F3&}圣父死了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.39,2:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.56,2:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧，教父\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sleep, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:27.94,2:21:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以进吗？{\fs12} [意大利语]{\r}\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Posso entrare io?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.53,2:22:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}说吧...告诉我
Dialogue: 0,2:22:26.13,2:22:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}你已失去了人们的信心
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.84,2:22:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}立足于民心就是立足烂泥
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.71,2:22:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}迈可尔·柯利昂尼的口信呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.40,2:23:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}它很重要 我必须口对耳告诉你
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.57,2:23:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}他没带武器
Dialogue: 0,2:23:29.99,2:23:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H99D7F4&}权力会耗尽没有权力的人
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.19,2:25:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问我现在能跟你谈谈吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Can I please talk to you now?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.61,2:25:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行，玛丽，时候不对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Not now Mary, it's not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.15,2:25:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就跟我父亲一样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're just like my father.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.16,2:25:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧，跟你的家人待在一起，走吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, stay with the family. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:29.37,2:25:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 跟我说吧  - 双胞胎都死了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Talk to me. -The twins are dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:31.37,2:25:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约一分钟后，就会有宪兵遍布这地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In about one minute there's going to be carbanieri crawling all over this place.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.34,2:25:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，带所有人上车，要不动声色\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay. Let's get everybody to the cars. Nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:39.54,2:25:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 收到  - 不动声色\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Got it. -Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:55.89,2:25:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他们听到柯利昂尼这个名字，就会想起那歌声\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}When they hear the name Corleone, they're going to think of that voice.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.79,2:26:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.34,2:26:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我妈妈\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is my mom.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:26.54,2:26:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你不必这样对我，求你  - 玛丽，快来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You don't have to do this to me, please. -Mary, come on...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:28.86,2:26:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 怎样对你，亲爱的，你在说什么？ - 快来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Doing what, sweetheart. What do you mean? -Come on...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:31.70,2:26:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽，请你…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Mary, please...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.00,2:26:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.76,2:27:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦不，不  - 哦，上帝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Oh, no, no! -Oh, god.
